title: Morlaix Communauté
text:
Morlaix Communauté is the "<a href="agglomeration%20community">agglomeration community</a>", an <a href="Communes%20of%20France%23Intercommunality">intercommunal</a> structure, centred on the <a href="Communes%20of%20France">city</a> of <a href="Morlaix">Morlaix</a>. It is located in the <a href="Finist%C3%A8re">Finistère</a> <a href="departments%20of%20France">department</a>, in the <a href="Brittany%20%28administrative%20region%29">Brittany</a> <a href="regions%20of%20France">region</a>, western <a href="France">France</a>. Its population was 64,304 in 2015, of which 14,830 in Morlaix proper.
